  "texts": [
    "In this section we present the settings we configured to run the ML models.",
    "The main parameters composing our ensemble solution and used to train the models are reported in Table 1.",
    "The dataset is a collection of temporal series of heterogeneous data acquired over the 27 FUs of Brazil, here defined as X ∈ R D×T×V where D represents the FUs, T the temporal length of the series, here expressed by 19 years of 12 months, and V the heterogeneous variables.",
    "To complete the dataset, the sum of DIR has been acquired for the same FUs, during the same temporal interval, and is defined as Y ∈ R D×T.",
    "The dataset is divided in training and validation by selecting data from 2001 to 2016 for the former and from 2017 to 2019 for the latter."
